On the fan-shaped west wall,

571
00:29:04,900 --> 00:29:06,540
there are inscribed

572
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:09,580
verses by the most famous poets
in Yong'an today.

573
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:18,540
Rich oily aroma.

574
00:29:19,140 --> 00:29:20,980
Steamed with light seasoning.

575
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,620
An expert!

576
00:29:22,620 --> 00:29:25,100
You really smell the specialties
of both of them.

577
00:29:26,140 --> 00:29:27,060
Thank you.

578
00:29:28,220 --> 00:29:29,140
Dad!

579
00:29:31,260 --> 00:29:33,180
Father, you're amazing.

580
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:35,300
You call this amazing?

581
00:29:35,860 --> 00:29:37,140
My goodness.

582
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:39,050
The chefs at Yunlai Tavern
prefer to cook

583
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:39,940
mainly with grilling

584
00:29:39,940 --> 00:29:41,020
and deep-frying.

585
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:43,140
Guixiang Tavern, on the other hand,
mostly uses steaming

586
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:44,500
to preserve the original flavor.

587
00:29:44,500 --> 00:29:45,450
The taste leans towards mild.

588
00:29:45,740 --> 00:29:46,780
If you ask me,

589
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:48,880
it's not particularly original either.

590
00:29:49,180 --> 00:29:51,140
Wait until my shop opens,

591
00:29:51,140 --> 00:29:52,860
the two of them combined

592
00:29:52,860 --> 00:29:53,780
won't be my match.

593
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,000
Bring me along...

594
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,940
Come here. What we want to see
is right up ahead.

595
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:58,860
Come.

596
00:29:59,420 --> 00:30:00,340
Mom,

597
00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:02,130
look at my dad, aren't you going
to do something?

598
00:30:03,380 --> 00:30:05,180
(Luo's Grocery Store)
This is the one.

599
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:07,060
Among the vacant shops in Juxian Alley,

600
00:30:07,220 --> 00:30:09,500
this one is the closest
to the city center.

601
00:30:09,660 --> 00:30:11,820
It only costs 400 qian per month.

602
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,880
- Remember,
- It looks alright.

603
00:30:12,900 --> 00:30:13,900
money isn't the problem.

604
00:30:14,620 --> 00:30:15,860
The problem is that

605
00:30:15,860 --> 00:30:17,380
this shop is too ordinary.

606
00:30:17,380 --> 00:30:18,540
Are there any better ones?

607
00:30:18,980 --> 00:30:19,900
Yes!

608
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:21,180
Isn't this pretty good?

609
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:22,100
This way, please.

610
00:30:24,140 --> 00:30:25,860
On the issue of choosing a shop,

611
00:30:25,860 --> 00:30:27,200
you need to firmly support me.

612
00:30:27,210 --> 00:30:28,100
How great is this one?

613
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:29,100
Right?

614
00:30:29,820 --> 00:30:31,100
Dad, if you'd said that earlier,

615
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:32,180
I would have understood.

616
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,100
You...

617
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:35,580
(Dried Fruit Shop)

618
00:30:35,580 --> 00:30:36,500
500 qian.

619
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:37,780
For this size?

620
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,740
Are there any better ones?

621
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:42,060
Any better ones?

622
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:43,420
Yes. There are.

623
00:30:43,780 --> 00:30:45,580
Take me to see them. Let's go.

624
00:30:45,580 --> 00:30:46,500
This way.

625
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:51,540
(Jinxiu Tavern)
Among the vacant shops in Juxian Alley,

626
00:30:51,540 --> 00:30:53,540
this is the largest and best one.

627
00:30:53,540 --> 00:30:55,260
800 qian per month.

628
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:56,180
Too small.

629
00:30:56,820 --> 00:30:58,300
Still too small.

630
00:30:58,700 --> 00:31:00,460
Still too small!

631
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:02,820
Shen Jianshe.

632
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:04,420
Shen Shaojie.

633
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,260
You two, come here.

634
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:07,660
What?

635
00:31:10,660 --> 00:31:12,340
Wait. What's wrong now?

636
00:31:12,340 --> 00:31:13,740
I'm busy here.

637
00:31:13,740 --> 00:31:15,620
Time is money.

638
00:31:16,620 --> 00:31:17,820
Shen Jianshe,

639
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:19,540
have you gotten above yourself?

640
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:21,100
- Have you gotten above yourself?
- I haven't.

641
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,700
Have you decided what scale
you want to open?

642
00:31:22,700 --> 00:31:24,240
And there you are, picking and choosing.

643
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,820
You think a two-story building is small?

644
00:31:25,820 --> 00:31:26,860
Do you want to ascend to heaven?

645
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:27,670
I... I haven't.

646
00:31:27,670 --> 00:31:29,860
I'm using tactics.

647
00:31:29,860 --> 00:31:30,920
Do you have the brains for that?

648
00:31:30,940 --> 00:31:31,820
Tactics?

649
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:33,180
Yes. Dad, don't make excuses.

650
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:34,160
You definitely have a problem.

651
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:35,200
And you, Shen Shaojie.

652
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,300
- Mom!
- Why are you joining in?

653
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:37,540
- Why are you joining in?
- My fault.

654
00:31:37,540 --> 00:31:38,410
Dear, just hit him!

655
00:31:38,420 --> 00:31:40,460
Can you let go of me first?

656
00:31:41,220 --> 00:31:42,120
I'm telling you two,

657
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:43,220
keep your mouths shut later.

658
00:31:43,220 --> 00:31:44,140
Did you hear me?

659
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:45,940
- I hear you.
- I hear you.

660
00:31:47,620 --> 00:31:48,540
Grandma!

661
00:31:51,980 --> 00:31:52,900
Ma'am,

662
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:54,540
sorry about this.

663
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:55,420
Could you please

664
00:31:55,420 --> 00:31:56,740
help us find another place?

665
00:31:56,740 --> 00:31:58,300
The location doesn't need
to be too prominent.

666
00:31:58,300 --> 00:31:59,850
The building doesn't need
to be too big either.

667
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:02,340
You should have said so earlier.

668
00:32:02,540 --> 00:32:03,460
Of course, I can.

669
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,120
Money.

670
00:32:07,120 --> 00:32:08,640
Money is something you still need to...

671
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:10,020
Come. Look at this one.

672
00:32:12,220 --> 00:32:14,460
This originally belonged
to Councilor Kang's family.

673
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,500
He has many properties.

674
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:16,410
This one is small.

675
00:32:16,410 --> 00:32:17,780
He doesn't pay it much attention.

676
00:32:17,780 --> 00:32:18,620
Only 300 qian

677
00:32:18,620 --> 00:32:19,900
per month.

678
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:22,060
However, there's one condition.

679
00:32:22,260 --> 00:32:23,380
Councilor Kang

680
00:32:23,380 --> 00:32:24,620
is a food enthusiast.

681
00:32:24,620 --> 00:32:26,500
So, he only wants to rent this

682
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:28,220
to people in the food business.

683
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:30,140
Who is Councilor Kang?

684
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:32,300
You don't know who Councilor Kang is?

685
00:32:32,360 --> 00:32:33,260
No.

686
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:35,180
He's the most famous food connoisseur

687
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:36,740
in all of Yong'an.

688
00:32:36,740 --> 00:32:39,100
Do you know about
the annual Culinary Master Competition?

689
00:32:39,500 --> 00:32:40,900
That's his creation.

690
00:32:41,860 --> 00:32:43,900
That competition, right?

691
00:32:44,780 --> 00:32:46,300
Ma'am, how about this?

692
00:32:46,300 --> 00:32:48,540
We'll pay you one year's rent upfront.

693
00:32:48,540 --> 00:32:49,940
Can you give us a little discount?

694
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:52,060
How about 250 qian per month?

695
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:54,860
Dear, have you thought this through?

696
00:32:55,140 --> 00:32:56,820
What kind of nonsense is this?

697
00:32:56,820 --> 00:32:59,180
Besides, 250 doesn't sound good either.

698
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:00,260
It's fine, it suits you.

699
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:02,460
280.

700
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:04,460
Really, there's no profit.

701
00:33:04,460 --> 00:33:06,500
You clearly look like
a straightforward person.

702
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,960
You definitely still
have room to negotiate.

703
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:08,860
Just 250.

704
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:10,420
265.

705
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:12,340
The backyard has a loft.

706
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:13,740
Although it's not renovated,

707
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:15,180
it can be used as a storeroom.

708
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:16,580
Let's settle for 250.

709
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,460
Alright.

710
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,940
You really know how to do business.

711
00:33:21,060 --> 00:33:22,220
Not at all.

712
00:33:22,220 --> 00:33:24,260
Let's just consider it
as forming a good connection.

713
00:33:24,460 --> 00:33:25,540
This shop

714
00:33:25,540 --> 00:33:26,740
is truly a bargain.

715
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,940
That backyard connects to the alley.

716
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,700
When you expand later,

717
00:33:30,700 --> 00:33:32,780
it's like getting half a shop for free.

718
00:33:33,020 --> 00:33:33,940
Expand?

719
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,300
You can do that here?

720
00:33:36,300 --> 00:33:37,860
Wait, this isn't regulated?

721
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:38,820
Who regulates it?

722
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:41,220
Look how much
the Yunlai Tavern expanded.

723
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:43,260
It occupies half the back alley.

724
00:33:43,260 --> 00:33:44,700
And it's still doing fine, right?

725
00:33:44,980 --> 00:33:45,860
Don't worry.

726
00:33:45,860 --> 00:33:47,180
Nothing will go wrong.

727
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,260
Fine. Then...

728
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:50,460
We'll take this one.

729
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:52,260
Let's sign the contract.

730
00:33:52,260 --> 00:33:53,620
Yes. Let's sign it.

731
00:33:53,620 --> 00:33:54,540
Quickly. Let's go.

732
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:55,660
Let's go.

733
00:33:55,660 --> 00:33:59,860
(Yong'an)

734
00:33:59,860 --> 00:34:01,340
Young Master, what you just mentioned

735
00:34:01,820 --> 00:34:03,540
is about the shops in Juxian Alley

736
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,660
illegally expanding without permission.

737
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:09,140
Presumably, people must
have discovered it before.

738
00:34:09,140 --> 00:34:10,140
But why was it

739
00:34:10,140 --> 00:34:11,420
never dealt with?

740
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:13,100
Yong'an is

741
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:14,300
more complicated than it is outside.

742
00:34:15,150 --> 00:34:17,400
The interests behind the East
and West Markets are deeply entangled.

743
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:19,300
The case against Mr. Yun

744
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:20,460
for embezzlement was easy to solve.

745
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,420
But here,

746
00:34:23,420 --> 00:34:24,700
many people can't be touched.

747
00:34:25,540 --> 00:34:26,620
Exactly.

748
00:34:26,940 --> 00:34:27,900
For example,

749
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:30,140
the two most famous shops
in Juxian Alley are

750
00:34:30,380 --> 00:34:31,380
Guixiang Tavern

751
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:32,780
and Yunlai Tavern.

752
00:34:33,300 --> 00:34:34,700
They both have wealth and influence.

753
00:34:34,940 --> 00:34:35,980
If you really investigate,

754
00:34:35,980 --> 00:34:37,820
who knows who might be implicated
behind them?

755
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,260
How about

756
00:34:40,660 --> 00:34:43,220
you just make a token gesture?

757
00:34:44,620 --> 00:34:46,420
Since I'm the Vice Prefect
of the Capital Prefecture,

758
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:48,740
I can't hold office
without doing my duty.

759
00:34:49,580 --> 00:34:50,940
Come here. Jicai.

760
00:34:50,940 --> 00:34:52,660
Look at the shop we chose.

761
00:34:53,420 --> 00:34:54,420
Isn't it good?

762
00:34:54,620 --> 00:34:55,820
And it's quite big, too.

763
00:34:57,220 --> 00:34:58,460
Listen, Jicai,

764
00:34:58,460 --> 00:34:59,520
you need to quickly find someone

765
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:00,940
to make me a few cooking pots.

766
00:35:00,940 --> 00:35:01,860
The pots here

767
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,300
don't suit my hands well.

768
00:35:03,780 --> 00:35:05,580
There's still so much to be busy with.

769
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:06,600
Jicai,

770
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:07,760
you've always had good ideas.

771
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:08,620
Take a look.

772
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:10,020
How should we decorate this place?

773
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,380
By the way, Jicai,

774
00:35:11,420 --> 00:35:12,260
that broker said

775
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:14,180
we could expand a bit more here.

776
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:16,260
Of course, I'm afraid
we might get investigated.

777
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:17,860
You decide.

778
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:19,860
You guys decide. I'm fine with anything.

779
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:21,820
Auntie,

780
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:23,420
you seem a bit unhappy.

781
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,500
Do you still want to go back
to the modern era?

782
00:35:27,140 --> 00:35:28,620
Here's a lollipop for you.

783
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:32,900
Thanks, Yangyang.

784
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:34,700
Jicai,

785
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:35,940
you need to accept reality.

786
00:35:36,170 --> 00:35:37,000
Think about it carefully.

787
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,020
That little restaurant of ours

788
00:35:38,020 --> 00:35:39,100
was bound to go bankrupt.

789
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:40,260
What would we even go back to?

790
00:35:40,260 --> 00:35:41,820
What is there worth missing?

791
00:35:41,820 --> 00:35:42,660
Huh?

792
00:35:42,660 --> 00:35:43,720
Is it that account of yours

793
00:35:43,780 --> 00:35:45,140
with only 200 followers?

794
00:35:45,140 --> 00:35:47,100
Or that "genius" ex-boyfriend of yours?

795
00:35:47,100 --> 00:35:48,020
That guy...

796
00:35:49,300 --> 00:35:50,260
Jicai,

797
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:52,620
I didn't think much
of this place at first either.

798
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:54,020
But thinking about it later,

799
00:35:54,020 --> 00:35:55,060
it's not bad.

800
00:35:55,060 --> 00:35:57,020
Think of our little restaurant
in the modern era,

801
00:35:57,020 --> 00:35:58,500
it wasn't even a third this size.

802
00:35:59,180 --> 00:36:00,700
This place can make money.

803
00:36:00,860 --> 00:36:02,580
And we have the ancestor blessing us.

804
00:36:02,780 --> 00:36:03,700
It's good.

805
00:36:03,700 --> 00:36:04,620
Yes.

806
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:05,940
Jicai,

807
00:36:07,140 --> 00:36:08,140
talk to me.

808
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:10,060
Why do you want to go back so badly?

809
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:12,020
Nothing.

810
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:14,740
It's okay. Say it.

811
00:36:14,740 --> 00:36:15,660
Don't bottle it up.

812
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:17,100
Bottling it up is so uncomfortable.

813
00:36:17,260 --> 00:36:18,180
Say it.

814
00:36:20,740 --> 00:36:22,260
I just can't understand.

815
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:24,660
How could we suddenly come to

816
00:36:24,660 --> 00:36:25,900
this godforsaken place?

817
00:36:27,700 --> 00:36:29,860
Before, I worked day and night
on side jobs.

818
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:32,380
I... I finally saved up a bit of money

819
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:33,940
and bought a dishwasher for our home.

820
00:36:34,660 --> 00:36:35,780
Over 3,000 yuan.

821
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,620
I never even used it once.

822
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:39,860
Here, trying to run a good business

823
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:40,940
still gets looked down upon.

824
00:36:40,940 --> 00:36:42,220
They called us the lower class.

825
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:43,620
During the day, I have to learn

826
00:36:43,620 --> 00:36:44,740
how to bow to others,

827
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:46,120
and I can't go out at night either.

828
00:36:46,180 --> 00:36:47,100
Yes.

829
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:48,500
We can sneak out.

830
00:36:49,100 --> 00:36:50,140
But it's sneaking.

831
00:36:50,140 --> 00:36:51,340
Not free at all.

832
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:53,100
You've all gotten used to it.

833
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:54,660
None of you wants to go back!

834
00:36:54,660 --> 00:36:55,580
Auntie.

835
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:56,940
Don't worry.

836
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,300
Take it slow.

837
00:36:58,620 --> 00:37:00,980
We've only just started here.

838
00:37:01,240 --> 00:37:02,230
Who knows, maybe one day,

839
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:03,780
we'll suddenly go back.

840
00:37:03,780 --> 00:37:06,500
Jicai, please don't worry.

841
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:07,740
This thing...

842
00:37:08,220 --> 00:37:09,580
You need to adapt slowly.

843
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:12,300
Yes. See, isn't everything
slowly getting on track?

844
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,830
Since we're here,
we should make the best of it.

845
00:37:14,830 --> 00:37:15,730
Since we can't go back,

846
00:37:15,730 --> 00:37:16,620
we'll just...

847
00:37:17,380 --> 00:37:18,300
Auntie.

848
00:37:19,260 --> 00:37:20,180
Maybe.

849
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:21,740
I'll adapt some more.

850
00:37:21,740 --> 00:37:22,780
I'll be fine in a few days.

851
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:25,580
Yes. You'll be fine in a few days.

